John Megna https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Megna 0 John Megna (November 9, 1952 – September 4, 1995) was an American actor. His best known role is that of "Dill" in the film To Kill a Mockingbird. John_Megna ( November_9_,_1952 – September_4_,_1995 ) was an_American_actor . His_best_known_role is that of " Dill " in the_film To_Kill a_Mockingbird .
